FOR SALE VIA EXPRESSIONS OF INTEREST CLOSING THURSDAY 29TH NOVEMBER AT 4.00PM (ACDT)

A premium Bluechip investment underpinned by a subsidiary of the ASX Listed Coca Cola Amatil Limited.

Located approximately 13Km north west of the Adelaide CBD, Can Recycling (S.A.) Pty Ltd use the facility for storage of recycled cans and have been occupying the site for over 20 years.

~ Modern office warehouse of 392 sqm* including quality concrete tilt-up construction, neat office area, high clearance warehouse, secure cage area, on-site parking and all with main road frontage.
